{"tid":2269171,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應港台編導被捕　梁家榮關注會否出現寒蟬效應 整個新聞界都應該認真看待","createTime":"2020-11-03T10:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T12:11:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"55e6e112921e4187f03f5733b7c829ad702301c3","tid":2269171,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:02:30.000Z","msg":"香港電台電視部編導蔡玉玲被警方拘捕。據了解，懷疑事件與蔡玉玲參與製作的《鏗鏘集：7.21誰主真相》報道有關，有人以不正當資料做車輛查冊，涉嫌違反《道路交通條例》。廣播處長梁家榮表示，關心同事被捕會否對香港電台新聞工作有非常大影響，會否出現寒蟬效應。<br />\n<br />\n梁家榮下午在廣播大廈接待外賓時，記者上前追訪，他表示，仍在了解事件，未清楚相關罪名及涉及的事件，管方正嘗試提供協助，但目前聯絡不到蔡玉玲。被問到記者因採訪被捕是否罕見，梁家榮形容今次事件確是少有，新聞工作者確會擔心，指若被捕控罪涉及採訪或搜集資料，整個新聞界都應該認真看待事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558142-20201103.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558142-20201103.htm&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbox6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=7fc81bb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558142-20201103.htm&h=a48083a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558142-20201103.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1339cfd3a3bf61d92a660bcf6bb775be74bbd07e","tid":2269171,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54419c74ead39dd8d744fc6f76429dbe6309812f","tid":2269171,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1339cfd3a3bf61d92a660bcf6bb775be74bbd07e","tid":2269171,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"h